{"tid":1546364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警惡毒情度同戰犯無分別, 除左官員之外, 制裁黑警係第二大目標","createTime":"2019-09-06T09:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:10:44.000Z","uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6df62afb238609395115a4a84ead5b007b38f09b","tid":1546364,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"警方本來就係維持治安, 而唔係解釋法律, 一個人有冇罪唔係由警方去制裁, 而係由法律去制裁.<br />\n<br />\n由所謂4點記者會, 黑警已經用佢地既法律去判罪, 由街頭用武力去判罪. 完全無視法律原意, 同所謂政治中立已經原全無關.<br />\n<br />\n假証供, 隱藏自己身份, 佢地都係為隱藏自己罪証而做, 毆打, 強姦, 殺人呢類嚴重罪行係由呢班所謂執法者去每日執行.<br />\n<br />\n呢班人已經唔係執法者, 除左香港官員外, 香港呢3萬名罪犯, 亦要高調要求外國制裁, 呢世都唔可以放過佢地."},{"pid":"03097e559c2c1dc5d6cfbe53806625773f0a9e1a","tid":1546364,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c3186a11961efea29428abe83debe516146bb8e","tid":1546364,"uid":149215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"［核彈]906全民太子站獻花，極重要！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544949</a>"},{"pid":"bbf423cef0071ec77fbd6a70db8c1102699a31db","tid":1546364,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"同意，仲有建制派"},{"pid":"119efbd384a85deb07a072311521a26b1ae86590","tid":1546364,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=30eb8446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"